{"tid":2263553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"脫阻街罪 男生籲毋忘手足","createTime":"2020-10-30T03:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T03:53:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"daa3986fbcdf96b983b77257d8adbe83462c761c","tid":2263553,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/6O6IJ22YFJEB7H6WM3WDKFCXPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2F6O6IJ22YFJEB7H6WM3WDKFCXPY%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=d6470b36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2F6O6IJ22YFJEB7H6WM3WDKFCXPY%2F&h=53fe1a74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/6O6IJ22YFJEB7H6WM3WDKFCXPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n脫阻街罪 男生籲毋忘手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/txI3lwwHjwqvAd14l65WvL6Ffww=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VHSE5IQCENHQREZ7KPII4S237E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtxI3lwwHjwqvAd14l65WvL6Ffww%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVHSE5IQCENHQREZ7KPII4S237E.jpg&h=6ebc9c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年11月11日黃大仙有人堵路，防暴出動清場。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中六男生去年全港「大三罷」當日早上，遇上警方驅散，及後被警員追截拘捕。他最初因涉嫌非法集結被捕，及後被控阻街罪，早前受審。裁判官昨指警員證供準確度成疑，加上法庭不肯定被告究竟是參與聚集堵路抑或僅屬路過，裁定罪名不成立。男生離庭時指本案屬濫捕濫告，並嘆謂社運案件開始不受社會關注，呼籲大眾：「唔好忘記其他手足。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱差館內聞被捕者遭警暴<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，拘捕被告的警員在草圖指出案發地點為沙田坳道與鳳德道交界，不符他本人的證供，作供準確度存疑。<br />\n<br />\n葉官表明，需考慮單憑警員證供便定罪的危險性。警員承認在驅散時。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張脫罪後在庭外形容警方「亂咁捉人」，又自言沒遭受警暴，但在警署內聽到與他同日被捕的人遭警員拳毆及扯耳朵。張寄語市民勿忘其他社運案件手足。<br />\n<br />\n張早前出庭自辯稱，當日在港鐵站外看見大量防暴警員，有警員指罵人群謂：「死曱甴，你走唔甩㗎喇，入去坐幾年啦！」警員及後衝向人群，張不想無故被捕，於是跑走，其間因書包阻礙速度而丟棄書包，最終被捕，警員未有在書包內搜出可疑物品。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC939/20"},{"pid":"4bfe35f1ea5ab05d90c3a59b992da0a6b287964d","tid":2263553,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">黑警見字死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"b971359164aa0a802560efd41d48c38beb5b7dba","tid":2263553,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:53:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">呼籲大眾：「唔好忘記其他手足。」</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1cd7ce7e1b2ddbabfdb95c8ac7b271c935d6c04b","tid":2263553,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"阻街罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n車房門口擺滿曬自己嘢算唔算阻街？"}]}